  "description": "10ms Rectangular window grains at density=90. The grain boundary clicks from the hard-windowed 10ms segments accumulate into metallic crunch at this density. The ear cannot resolve 10ms temporal structure — it hears the spectral content of the grain boundaries themselves as continuous texture. The boundary between time-domain and frequency-domain hearing is audible here.",
